description: Discover the comfort of this LARGE 1526sqft  3-bedroom, 2.5-bath townhome, which includes a large open-concept living and dining area perfect for daily living. The kitchen is equipped for  cooking efficiency, featuring updated appliances and ample counter space for entertaining. Each bedroom offers ample space easily fitting queen beds in all and King in two. The master boasting an en-suite bathroom and a sizable closet  for those with a large wardrobe.Added conveniences include a dedicated laundry room with storage and TWO DEEDED GARAGE PARKING  SPOTS ensuring ease of access and security for your vehiclesFor investor buyer please know this unit creaturely rents for $4500 per month.  That is a higher then 4% rate of return!!!!
